Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
The Booking class represents a booking made by a customer for a flight. It includes details such as the booking ID, customer, flight, price, booking date, and cancellation status, along with any applicable fees for cancellation or rebooking.
